@startuml failsafe_blocked_context_to_diag_path_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Failsafe Blocked Context To Diag Path Signal Flow\n(TEST_SCN -> CGW -> IVI / Test evidence)

actor "Validation Harness\n(TEST_SCN)" as Harness #F4F7FB
participant "TEST_SCN\nscenario/test driver" as TEST_SCN #FFE6E6
participant "CGW\ngateway fail-safe owner" as CGW #FFF4CC
participant "IVI\ninfo diagnostic mirror" as IVI #E8F0FE
participant "Diag sysvars /\nEVIDENCE_OUT" as Evidence #E8F7E8

== Fail-safe Stimulation ==

Harness -> TEST_SCN : forceFailSafe = 1\nor blocked-context scenario phase
activate TEST_SCN
TEST_SCN -> CGW : Core::forceFailSafe\n/ gateway observer conditions
note right of TEST_SCN
Representative test anchors
- ST_043 blocked context
- UT_063 blocked SGW context
- UT_064 blocked DCM context
- IT_040 integrated blocked context
end note
deactivate TEST_SCN

== CGW Blocked Context Decision ==

activate CGW
CGW -> CGW : derive warningPathStatus
CGW -> CGW : derive failSafeMode
CGW -> CGW : if failSafeMode >= 1\nthen decel assist gating applies
CGW -> CGW : publishFailSafeState()\npublishGatewayState()\npublishObjectSafetyState()
CGW -> CGW : CoreState::domainBoundaryStatus\nCoreState::warningPathStatus\nCore::failSafeMode
note right of CGW
Blocked context is represented by
warningPathStatus / failSafeMode
and exported over gateway/observer paths.
end note
CGW -> IVI : gateway / fail-safe state frames
CGW -> Evidence : CoreState::* / Core::failSafeMode
deactivate CGW

== Diagnostic / Evidence Surface ==

activate IVI
IVI -> IVI : InfoDiagState = 1\nInfoFailCode = 0 in base health publish
IVI -> Evidence : Diag::InfoDiagState\nDiag::InfoFailCode
deactivate IVI

activate Evidence
Evidence -> Evidence : TEST_SCN monitors\nnominal / degraded / blocked context
Evidence -> Evidence : gDiagCtxNominalSeen /\ngDiagCtxDegradedSeen /\ngDiagCtxBlockedSeen
Evidence -> Evidence : EVIDENCE_OUT log line includes\nfailSafeMode / warningPath / render code
deactivate Evidence

note over Harness, Evidence
Representative runtime chain
1. TEST_SCN forces a blocked fail-safe condition
2. CGW owns fail-safe mode and warning-path downgrade
3. Gateway state is mirrored into diag/info surfaces
4. TEST_SCN captures blocked-context evidence and verdict anchors
end note

@enduml
